    <p data-en="I'm Lavender Meadow — a professional beach volleyball player whose name is more than just a name. It's a philosophy. Like the flower that thrives in sun-scorched fields without rain, I've learned that resilience isn't about being unbreakable. It's about blooming anyway." data-fr="Je suis Lavender Meadow — une joueuse professionnelle de volleyball de plage dont le nom est bien plus qu'un simple nom. C'est une philosophie. Comme la fleur qui s'épanouit dans les champs brûlés de soleil sans pluie, j'ai appris que la résilience ne consiste pas à être inébranlable. C'est à s'épanouir malgré tout.">I'm Lavender Meadow — a professional beach volleyball player whose name is more than just a name. It's a philosophy. Like the flower that thrives in sun-scorched fields without rain, I've learned that resilience isn't about being unbreakable. It's about blooming anyway.</p>
